      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2193_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "5.(2016年全国Ⅰ卷）《荀·劝学》指出，蚯蚓虽然体柔弱，却能“ , ”,是专的缘故。",
        "bbox": [
          0.10190084264158339,
